data.value:
Netsky Antivirus 2015, version 1.0
Developed using C#, .NET 4.0 Uses C compiled engines for scanning
Designed and Developed by: Romil Kr. Gupta, Shantanu Choudhary, Sonam Jindal, Puja Kumari,Shalini Arya, Rajnish Kumar, Shailza Choudhary, Sarthak Jain, Mohitanshu Sharma, Tejashwi Kalp Taru, Ntambala Manda, Somya Shrivastav Suraiya Jabeen and Rajat Singh
This program is developed for the Summer project in Sharda University, School of Engineering and Technology (India)
This system is just a prototype of actual antivirus and currently it's in testing. Kindly don't depend on this system for your PC security.
